{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Universality.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.universality\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">WickAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">universality</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">A</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#Semiring\">Semiring</a> <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Defs.html#Algebra\">Algebra</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a> <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.CrAnFieldOp\">CrAnFieldOp</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h1</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ <span class=\"fn\">a</span> ∈ <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/TwoSidedIdeal/Operations.html#TwoSidedIdeal.span\">TwoSidedIdeal.span</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.fieldOpIdealSet\">fieldOpIdealSet</a></span></span>, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/FreeAlgebra.html#FreeAlgebra.lift\">FreeAlgebra.lift</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">f</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/ExistsUnique.html#ExistsUnique\">∃!</a> <span class=\"fn\">g</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/ExistsUnique.html#ExistsUnique\">:</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra\">WickAlgebra</a></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Hom.html#AlgHom\">→ₐ[</a><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Hom.html#AlgHom\">]</a> <span class=\"fn\">A</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/ExistsUnique.html#ExistsUnique\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\">⇑<span class=\"fn\">g</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Function.comp\">∘</a> <span class=\"fn\">⇑<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι\">ι</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">⇑<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/FreeAlgebra.html#FreeAlgebra.lift\">FreeAlgebra.lift</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">f</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification, `𝓕`, the algebra `𝓕.WickAlgebra` satisfies the following universal\nproperty. Let `f : 𝓕.CrAnFieldOp → A` be a function and `g : 𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra →ₐ[ℂ] A`\nthe universal lift of that function associated with the free algebra `𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra`.\nIf `g` is zero on the ideal defining `𝓕.WickAlgebra`, then there exists\nalgebra map `g' : WickAlgebra 𝓕 →ₐ[ℂ] A` such that `g' ∘ ι = g`, and furthermore this\nalgebra map is unique.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Universality.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.universality","kind":"theorem","line":75,"name":"FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.universality","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L75-L94"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Universality.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.universalLift_ι\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">WickAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">universalLift_ι</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">a</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">A</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#Semiring\">Semiring</a> <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Defs.html#Algebra\">Algebra</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a> <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.CrAnFieldOp\">CrAnFieldOp</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">h1</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ <span class=\"fn\">a</span> ∈ <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/TwoSidedIdeal/Operations.html#TwoSidedIdeal.span\">TwoSidedIdeal.span</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.fieldOpIdealSet\">fieldOpIdealSet</a></span></span>, <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/FreeAlgebra.html#FreeAlgebra.lift\">FreeAlgebra.lift</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">f</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">0</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Universality.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.universalLift\">universalLift</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">h1</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.WickAlgebra.ι\">ι</a> <span class=\"fn\">a</span>)</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/FreeAlgebra.html#FreeAlgebra.lift\">FreeAlgebra.lift</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">f</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">a</span></span></div></div>"